WEBVTT

00:01.769 --> 00:04.111
check this in just a minute and see if we are. Okay, 
if you'll begin by telling me your name and where

00:04.151 --> 00:08.856
you were born. Well, I was born in Musquis, 
Coahuila, Mexico. And my name was given to me was

00:16.063 --> 00:21.748
Guadalupe Garza. Then my mother and my daddy come 
to the United States in In August the 26th, 1926, we

00:31.030 --> 00:37.336
passed through Eagle Pass. And since then, we've 
been given in the United States. Yeah, I mean in

00:41.440 --> 00:44.162
Texas since then. And then we grew up over here in 
the, what you call, the brass bottom. And we went to

00:50.248 --> 00:52.810
school over there. We were 12 in the family, six 
boys and six girls. And my daddy was... farmer or

01:00.882 --> 01:30.163
agriculture, we used to plant cotton, corn in the 
fields, and we used to help them during the, not

01:00.882 --> 01:30.163
during the school period, but during the harvest, 
we used to help them and pull the cotton, pick the

01:00.882 --> 01:30.163
cotton, and then my, every year, you know, at the 
end of the year, my daddy will equalize the whole

01:00.882 --> 01:30.163
crop and then give them money, But I think those 
days were happy days to us. And all of my brothers

01:36.008 --> 01:40.092
and sisters, we all went to school. We got all that 
good education. I mean, not high school, but some

01:43.236 --> 01:50.283
got towards ninth grade, 10th grade, in those 
days. And I think that was good. And so all my family

01:53.887 --> 01:59.593
moved to the state of Oklahoma. And they all live 
over there except me. I live here. But then I got

02:03.549 --> 02:06.252
married in 1942. I got married to Mr. Medina. And 
then we... What is his first name? Julio. Julio

02:13.740 --> 02:14.762
Medina. Julio C. Contreras Medina. And he works at 
the MSC as a cook. He's doing a little vacation in

02:23.031 --> 02:25.734
Mexico. Oh, yeah. Yeah, he's there. They called 
this morning from... from close to Monterrey. My

02:32.778 --> 02:35.561
daughter and my son-in-law, they went over there. 
So then my daddy, before he come to the United

02:36.042 --> 02:50.436
States, he was born in Muscas, also in the same 
state and the same city we were born. What did his

02:51.317 --> 02:53.679
father do in Muscas? That would be your 
grandfather.

