06:01.202 --> 06:04.146
happen. But I really wanted to tell him that he was 
the one that went over there. But I don't know who I

06:10.073 --> 06:11.435
am. I kind of put it off every time I get a 
conversation. I want to tell him, but I don't know.

06:18.764 --> 06:24.632
I have to go and tell him that he was the first man 
